# Licensing Matrix

Copyright © 2026 Stephen Chia-Cheng Hsu.
Chinese name: 許家誠
Contact: [chiacheng.hsu@owasp.org](mailto:chiacheng.hsu@owasp.org)
GitHub: https://github.com/jiachengx

This repository uses layered licensing so that public examples, schemas, policies, and templates can be widely reused, while core governance tools remain open when redistributed.

This project is released as an open reference implementation for CID-based reference consistency governance in static publishing and offline content governance environments.

