## SPDX identifiers

Where practical, source files should include SPDX headers.

Use the romanized author name in SPDX headers for better compatibility with automated license scanners, package metadata, citation tools, and software bill-of-materials workflows.

For GPL-licensed core files:

```text
SPDX-FileCopyrightText: 2026 Stephen Chia-Cheng Hsu
SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later
```

For MIT-licensed example, schema, policy, UI-template, or test files:

```text
SPDX-FileCopyrightText: 2026 Stephen Chia-Cheng Hsu
SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT
```

For documentation:

```text
SPDX-FileCopyrightText: 2026 Stephen Chia-Cheng Hsu
SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-SA-4.0
```

